*<Obey$Dir>.Utils.CmdToVar Territory$Str Territory
*Set WOLSetup$Flag 0
*If "<WakeOnLAN$Dir>" = ""  Then Set WOLSetup$Flag 1
*If "<WOLSetup$Flag>" = "1" Then Set WakeOnLAN$Dir <Obey$Dir>
*If "<WOLSetup$Flag>" = "1" Then IconSprites <WakeOnLAN$Dir>.Resources.<Territory$Str>.!Sprites
*If "<WOLSetup$Flag>" = "1" Then Alias WakeOnLAN <WakeOnLAN$Dir>.bin.WakeOnLAN %%0
*Unset WOLSetup$Flag
*Unset Territory$Str

